{"title":"火热的钢厂","authors":["宁宇"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":9,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"火热的钢厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁　宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢厂的空气，火辣滚烫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢厂的大地，翻腾热浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢厂的钟声，连绵不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢厂的工人，脾气似钢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼钢炉前一站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身都冒火光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大干呵快上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶座座矿山进炉膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤十二级狂飚从天降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁掉一斤肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不少一两钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨不得——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢山铁岭在身旁猛劲长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大干呵快上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧！流水线上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞奔的蓝色钢板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多象舰艇在远航——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在惊涛骇浪的大洋中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的钢正乘风破浪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设需要钢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"备战需要钢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起探火镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼看四方——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里钢管走石油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里钢轨挽边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万吨钢闸锁高峡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在稻海麦浪中唱……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援世界革命呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要钢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要钢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为巩固无产阶级专政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——打物质基础；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为建设共产主义大厦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——浇桩基柱梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行车展翅飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊包飞快装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢锭站起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢材争出厂……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！是祖国一日千里脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是出钢钟声日夜响？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当当！当当！当当！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}